  "keyFeatures": [
    "CLI tool for generating TypeScript clients from OpenAPI specifications",
    "Production-ready SDKs with type safety",
    "20+ plugins including Zod schemas and TanStack Query hooks",
    "Support for multiple HTTP clients (Fetch, Axios, Angular, Next.js, Nuxt)",
    "Validators integration (Zod, Valibot)",
    "State management hooks for TanStack Query and Pinia Colada",
    "Highly customizable plugin system",
    "Watch mode for development",
    "OpenAPI 2.0, 3.0, and 3.1 support"
